# Build output
out/

# Must be manually extracted from your device
tools/framework-res.apk

# Uncomment if you ever switch to a real release keystore
# tools/release.keystore
```

`framework-res.apk` is the only file you **cannot** commit — it's a system file pulled from the device, and its exact version needs to match the ROM you're targeting. You get it with:
```
adb pull /system/framework/framework-res.apk tools/framework-res.apk